channel.title: I want to learn Java
channel.description: Hello, I have been messing with RSPS sources for a few years now, on and off. I am quite tired of not knowing what I am doing and having to constantly consult the forums. I've decided to just learn the language so I can help myself. So getting to the point... is there a section of Java I should learn that relates to RSPS? Should I just learn all of Java? Where can I learn it?
